Params: {1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/Bgstory178.png'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Luna', 3: "Still too naive, am I? I'm sorry, Sister.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'α', 3: "Happens to me too, no matter... Let's deal with these uninvited guests.", 4: '2'}
{3: 'No less than 30 humanoid Constructs stand before the two, with even more bionic machines behind. Alpha scans the room before settling her gaze on the female in the center.'}
{1: '1', 2: 'α', 3: "Luna, let the amassed Corrupted go elsewhere. They won't be of use here.", 4: '2'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Diana', 3: "Unfazed, aren't you... You must be Alpha.", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'α', 3: "And you must be the Forest Guards. I don't remember you being such partygoers.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'α', 3: 'Why here? Why the Gray Ravens?', 4: '1'}
{3: 'Alpha and Diana rest their hands on their weapons at the same time, readying for a fight to break out.'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Diana', 3: 'And what of you? You came out of nowhere and stripped us of our everyday lives. What are you up to now?!', 4: '1'}
{2: 'α', 3: "I see. You hold a grudge. It's about Rosetta...", 4: '2'}
{3: 'Hearing Alpha utter that name, Diana catapults her javelin. Alpha deflects the murderous projectile with the sheath of her sword.'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Diana', 3: 'You have no right to mention her... Forest Guards! Spears up!', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Forest Guard Member', 3: 'Roger!'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Luna', 3: "There's no avoiding battle, is it? Do you not feel pathetic to be fighting for humans who have once betrayed you?", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Diana', 3: "You are the lamentable ones. You Ascendants borrow the power of the Punishing Virus to destroy what you desire, and crush everyone's hopes.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Diana', 3: 'And what do you gain from that?!', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Diana', 3: "I don't know what history that city behind me bears, but you are the ones who left it in tatters, aren't you?", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Diana', 3: 'We—humanity—finally found a chance to understand each other again, but you lot keep standing in our way...', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'α', 3: 'So you believe in the tall tale that Babylonia wove. You believe in reconnecting the world.', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Diana', 3: "And that's why we hurried here.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Diana', 3: 'To make the world one again.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Diana', 3: 'Control your mechs and target the figure behind Alpha!', 4: '1'}
